http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/%E2%80%98Ensure-awards-for-meritorious-only%E2%80%99/article14006440.ece

Collector P. Lakshmi Narasimham on Monday ordered the district officials not to recommend those who were not worthy for presentation of awards and meritorious certificates on Republic Day. The Collector, who reviewed arrangements for Republic Day at KR Stadium, said that the there should not be any controversy after presentation of awards.The district administration observed that several persons were able to get meritorious certificates by lobbying. Some times, changes were being made at the eleventh hour.Mr. Narasimham wanted a check on all such malpractices and underlined the need for honouring the persons with good track record. Meanwhile, the attendance of people for Grievances Day was thin due to extended festival holidays. Only a few people turned up at the Collectorate with their grievances as majority of the employees were absent.